com.strategyobject.substrateclient.storage

Interface KeyHashingAlgorithm

  • All Known Implementing Classes:
    Blake2B128Concat, Identity, TwoX64Concat

    public interface KeyHashingAlgorithm
    An algorithm that's used to generate storage map's key. As a general rule it should be a transparent algorithm since non-transparent hashers are deprecated in Substrate.

      • hashSize

        int hashSize()
